      <ul><li>(i)   Partials rely heavily on configuration over convention</li><li>(ii)  Partials help DRY out different views which use similar content</li><li>(iii) A partial can access all of the same variables as the view that includes it</li><li>(iv)  Partial files must begin with an underscore</li></ul></p>
